    <briefdescription>
<para>SMBus callback structure. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Used to register a callback in the driver instance callback list. As many callbacks as needed can be added as long as each of them is a unique pointer of struct <ref refid="structsmbus__callback" kindref="compound">smbus_callback</ref>.</para>
<para>Note: Such struct should not be allocated on stack. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
